&lt;p&gt;Contact Michael Puckey or Peter Church at Michael.puckey@nbt.nhs.uk / Peter.church@nbt.nhs.uk or call 0117 4144502 to arrange a visit or have an informal discussion about our ICU opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
